     -b2-  (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A house:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the following saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA daAra fiY fikoriYnuzuwluka fiY","text_ar":"مَا دَارَ فِى فِكْرِىنُزُولُكَ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakoriY","text_ar":"وَكْرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thine alighting at my house was not revolved in my mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakiyrapN","text_ar":"وَكِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroD","text_ar":"فَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanodap","text_ar":"زَنْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frD","text_ar":"فرض"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["K","T","TA","As","S","A","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}